## ObjectEntry type

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export type ObjectEntry<T extends object> = [
  Keys<T> extends infer K
    ? T extends readonly unknown[]
      ? K extends number
        ? K
        : never
      : K
    : never,
  T[Keys<T>]
]
```
<b>References:</b> [Keys](./types-kit.keys.md)

## Example


```ts
type Foo = { a:1, b:2 }

// Expect: ['a' | 'b', 1 | 2]
type EntryType = ObjectEntry<Foo>
```
